1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 18

2
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,310
Zhao Jun?

3
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,280
You're her aunt?

4
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:41,280
Zhao Jun is excellent

5
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:42,710
and has her vocational degree.

6
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:44,040
I helped her

7
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,920
find a new job.

8
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,590
Good pay.

9
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:46,510
Just a bit tiring.

10
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:48,310
I thought she couldn't handle it.

11
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,510
But she insisted.

12
00:01:50,230 --> 00:01:51,310
Why didn't you tell me

13
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,840
you're her aunt?

14
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,950
She's a relative,

15
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,510
but the situation is complicated.

16
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,120
Well,

17
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,350
can you help me find her?

18
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:01,040
No problem.

19
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:01,920
Just leave it to me.

20
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,120
She knows my address.

21
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:03,790
Tell her

22
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,840
to come before dinner.

23
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,760
Today?

24
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:07,840
Yes.

25
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,750
It's New Year's Eve.

26
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,470
Can't an auntie invite her niece

27
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:12,240
for dinner?

28
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:12,680
No.

29
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,800
But this is so last minute!

30
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:16,280
What if I can't find her?

31
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,960
You just said

32
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:18,960
it's no problem.

33
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,280
But you didn't say it was for today!

34
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:23,430
Forget it.

35
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,840
Hey, hold on.

36
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:27,710
I'll try.

37
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,240
But

38
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:32,000
if I do find her,

39
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,310
you have to be home.

40
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,630
I don't want another repeat

41
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,400
of you tricking me

42
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,360
and bailing.

43
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:42,190
I know, I was out of line.

44
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,680
But that's on you.

45
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,560
You investigated me!

46
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:47,910
Now that

47
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:48,910
you're helping me,

48
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,470
let's forget about that.

49
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,870
And if you want,

50
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,080
you can come

51
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,310
with Zhao Jun.

52
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,590
Good idea.

53
00:03:00,710 --> 00:03:01,630
However,

54
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:03,470
I have to turn down

55
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,590
three other invitations.

56
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,080
That's kinda hard.

57
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,430
It's fine.

58
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,400
Suit yourself.

59
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:13,280
Well, count me in.

60
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,240
Two people hardly make a feast,

61
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:15,750
right?

62
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,310
We can.

63
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,470
You'd have to turn down three invitations.

64
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:19,240
What a hassle.

65
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:17,190
Coming!

66
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,720
Why are you so...

67
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,480
Didn't expect me, did you?

68
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,870
You've spent

69
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,310
three Spring Festivals alone.

70
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,630
Come in.

71
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,390
I know you're busy

72
00:04:37,510 --> 00:04:38,190
and swamped.

73
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,720
But I have time now.

74
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,240
The Jing River Bridge project

75
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,190
is finished.

76
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:46,160
And it's already open to traffic.

77
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:49,000
So my role as project director

78
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:50,630
is done.

79
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,560
After the holiday,

80
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,510
I'll be working at

81
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:56,830
the Political Consultative Conference.

82
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,800
So I asked for leave.

83
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,040
I said I have to

84
00:05:03,310 --> 00:05:04,160
go to Shenzhen

85
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,950
and spend this holiday

86
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:08,070
with my daughter.

87
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:12,190
I called home.

88
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:14,390
No one answered, right?

89
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:16,600
Yu is getting old.

90
00:05:17,310 --> 00:05:19,120
So her daughter took her

91
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,040
to the countryside.

92
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,240
Before she left,

93
00:05:21,310 --> 00:05:22,240
she made plenty of

94
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,310
your favorites.

95
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,430
Pickles.

96
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,120
Chili sauce.

97
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,870
Just the flavor

98
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:30,270
you loved as a kid.

99
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,160
Dad.

100
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,920
During your toughest times,

101
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,070
I wasn't there for you.

102
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,560
I couldn't even...

103
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:04,830
sit down

104
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,560
and listen to you.

105
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,720
Do you blame me?

106
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,310
Dad.

107
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,800
Dad.

108
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,240
Sorry.

109
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:34,070
Don't say that.

110
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:50,680
I thought

111
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,240
you were alone.

112
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:53,360
If you hadn't come,

113
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,950
I would be alone.

114
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:56,600
My niece

115
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,720
from Shenxian Peak

116
00:06:58,870 --> 00:06:59,920
was supposed to come,

117
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,630
but I don't think she will.

118
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,120
You keep in touch

119
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,830
with them quite a bit?

120
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,560
Don't misunderstand.

121
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,750
Just a poor choice of words.

122
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,390
Blood is thicker than water.

123
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:19,950
You're doing the right thing.

124
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,630
I support you.

125
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:24,800
Looks like

126
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,920
no one is coming today.

127
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,240
It's just you and me

128
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,160
for the reunion meal.

129
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:30,560
Great.

130
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,040
Be careful.

131
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,190
Delicious?

132
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:39,870
Very delicious.

133
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,070
Didn't taste

134
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,270
your cooking last time.

135
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,310
This is the first time

136
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,040
I've tried your cooking.

137
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,480
Please try it.

138
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:49,720
Here I go.

139
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,680
My cooking's gotten better.

140
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,630
Hello?

141
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,600
You're at the door?

142
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,070
Why are you calling?

143
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,680
Where's Zhao Jun?

144
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,190
Tried everything I could,

145
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,160
but couldn't find her.

146
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,070
I left her messages

147
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,040
through a few leads.

148
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:17,600
Maybe she will come when she sees them.

149
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,120
Fine.

150
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:20,920
Sorry.

151
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,070
I'm leaving.

152
00:08:23,270 --> 00:08:24,800
Hey, don't go!

153
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,830
Since you're here,

154
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,270
stay for the meal.

155
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,070
You...

156
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,080
Call me Mr. Meng.

157
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,120
I came from Guizhou.

158
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:36,390
I brought some of
the famous Guizhou liquor.

159
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,910
Come in. Let's have a few drinks.

160
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:38,550
No, thanks.

161
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:39,790
I'm driving.

162
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,200
He...

163
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:43,960
Uh, go inside.

164
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,320
Fine.

165
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,550
I'll join you

166
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:47,440
and move the car

167
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,360
when I'm sober.

168
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:49,270
Attaboy!

169
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:49,750
Come on.

170
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:50,270
Go in.

171
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:50,720
Well.

172
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,630
I'll help myself.

173
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,630
Come in, please.

174
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,240
Boy,

175
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,510
what's your name?

176
00:08:58,390 --> 00:08:59,240
I'm Gao Xiang.

177
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:00,600
Xiang means flying high.

178
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:01,750
How old are you?

179
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,870
I'm two years older than her.

180
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,720
What's your job?

181
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,150
I teach at an academy.

182
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:10,200
A teacher?

183
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,910
Also the vice principal.

184
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:13,360
I handle admissions, logistics,

185
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,320
and some classes.

186
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,960
So you're an all-rounder!

187
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,870
Not at all.

188
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,240
I'm not much of a drinker.

189
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,320
Hope I don't

190
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,120
let you down.

191
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,390
Me neither.

192
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,720
My daughter is better.

193
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:25,320
Then why don't you pour me some?

194
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:25,840
Well,

195
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,440
alright.

196
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,870
I'll pour you some.

197
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,080
Enough.

198
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,630
You're...

199
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,030
My dad.

200
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:38,030
Fang Wanzhi,

201
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:38,960
why didn't you

202
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,390
tell me this?

203
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,240
I didn't bring a gift.

204
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,200
Not her fault.

205
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,600
I hid it deliberately.

206
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,080
Wanted to surprise her.

207
00:09:47,870 --> 00:09:48,510
Gao,

208
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,720
now that

209
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,150
we're here,

210
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,790
we're friends.

211
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:55,240
Let's have a toast.

212
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:55,790
Okay?

213
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,080
Sure.

214
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,360
Cheers.

215
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:57,150
Cheers.

216
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,120
Happy New Year!

217
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,240
Happy New Year!

218
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:00,750
What is it

219
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,200
about Shenzhen

220
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:04,150
that we should learn from?

221
00:10:04,670 --> 00:10:05,960
The concept you just mentioned

222
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:06,840
is brilliant.

223
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,320
Shenzhen speed.

224
00:10:09,510 --> 00:10:10,150
This very idea

225
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:10,960
is worth

226
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,240
promoting across the mainland.

227
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,840
Can you talk about

228
00:10:13,910 --> 00:10:15,440
something interesting?

229
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:16,750
This is a great topic.

230
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,720
Gao's words

231
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,600
were profound.

232
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:20,510
I found it

233
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:21,510
truly inspiring.

234
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:24,670
Shenzhen really knows

235
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,510
how to nurture talent.

236
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:27,960
I'm flattered.

237
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,150
Hey,

238
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,000
Wanzhi,

239
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,200
he's outstanding.

240
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:34,000
You should learn from him.

241
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,790
Got it.

242
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:36,440
I will.

243
00:10:36,550 --> 00:10:37,360
A toast to you.

244
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,600
Cheers.

245
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,080
Alright then.

246
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,910
You two go on.

247
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,360
I'm off to get red packets.

248
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:47,480
What?

249
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:49,320
It's a Cantonese custom.

250
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:50,840
During the Spring Festival,

251
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:51,790
unmarried people

252
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,080
can ask for red packets.

253
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,150
I've lived in Shenzhen for two years.

254
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,200
If I don't go, they'll be upset.

255
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,630
I also need to give kids

256
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,510
red packets.

257
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,390
Bye.

258
00:11:01,670 --> 00:11:02,320
Go ahead.

259
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:03,480
Gao will keep me company.

260
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:07,320
Ms. Fang, wishing you prosperity!

261
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,630
Happy New Year!

262
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:11,150
Happy New Year! Wishing you prosperity!

263
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,440
Wishing you prosperity!

264
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,600
Happy New Year!

265
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:16,960
Here! Happy New Year!

266
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,150
Good luck and prosperity!

267
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:21,790
Pei!

268
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:22,960
Pei!

269
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,790
Ms. Fang,

270
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,270
prosperity to you!

271
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,030
You're a big boss now.

272
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,440
But I still need

273
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:30,480
to give you a red packet.

274
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:32,550
Thank you, Pei. Prosperity to you!

275
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:33,510
You're welcome.

276
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,000
When you make it big,

277
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,240
rent a few more rooms from me.

278
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:38,240
No problem.

279
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:53,200
Zhao Jun.

280
00:11:55,870 --> 00:11:56,510
Fang...

281
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:02,910
Why didn't you go to Shenxian Peak?

282
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:05,240
Double pay for working now.

283
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:06,630
It's been a year.

284
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:08,630
Why didn't you come find me?

285
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:11,000
No particular reason.

286
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:12,960
Then why did you come now?

287
00:12:13,870 --> 00:12:14,960
A few classmates told me

288
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,030
Mr. Gao was looking for me.

289
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:17,720
They left this address.

290
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:19,200
Mr. Gao

291
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,120
is here?

292
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,390
So I mean less

293
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:22,840
to you than an outsider?

294
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,670
There's a reunion dinner upstairs.

295
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:28,910
I made it.

296
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,200
If you'd like some,

297
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,320
just join us.

298
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,510
If not,

299
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,750
suit yourself.

300
00:12:37,630 --> 00:12:39,320
No one's ever cared about me.

301
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,600
In Shenxian Peak,

302
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,320
no one noticed whether I was at the table

303
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,510
during a reunion dinner.

304
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,000
Never imagined in Shenzhen,

305
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,510
someone would think of me.

306
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,000
Silly girl.

307
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,080
Say something nice.

308
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,030
Happy New Year.

309
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,200
Best of luck.

310
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:20,910
Prosperity to you.

311
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:26,870
Take it.

312
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:28,790
Let's go.

313
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,200
The sausages are ready.

314
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,240
Move over.

315
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,320
Come on.

316
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:55,750
Let's eat.

317
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,240
Zhao Jun,

318
00:13:58,870 --> 00:14:00,030
why are you still standing?

319
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,510
Take a seat.

320
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,390
Why are you staring at me?

321
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,670
This is your aunt's home.

322
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:08,720
Come on.

323
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:11,390
Sit here.

324
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,910
Alright, we can start now.

325
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,670
Too bad there's

326
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,870
only one fish.

327
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:19,550
It's fine.

328
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,480
Slide it, and it's whole.

329
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,120
What a great idea!

330
00:14:23,270 --> 00:14:23,960
Slide it then.

331
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,200
Ready?

332
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:29,150
One. Two. Three.

333
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:30,630
Good!

334
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,720
Well,

335
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:35,240
the feast begins again.

336
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:37,960
Can you drink?

337
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,120
No.

338
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:40,150
I'll teach you.

339
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:41,120
Here.

340
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:42,360
Your cup.

341
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:45,200
Zhao Jun,

342
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,910
we Chinese

343
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,550
treasure Spring Festival the most.

344
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:49,960
So you can

345
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,150
have a little today.

346
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,200
If you get drunk,

347
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,720
just stay

348
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,840
the night here.

349
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,120
I booked a room

350
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,720
at the guesthouse

351
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:58,790
next door.

352
00:14:59,360 --> 00:14:59,750
Gao,

353
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,790
you had some too.

354
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:01,720
Come stay

355
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:03,030
at the guesthouse with me.

356
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:03,720
Okay?

357
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:04,870
Good idea.

358
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:05,840
Then you two

359
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:06,670
can continue

360
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,600
your conversation

361
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:08,390
about Shenzhen.

362
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,270
Exactly!

363
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:10,910
Come on,

364
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:12,120
my family!

365
00:15:12,670 --> 00:15:14,030
Happy New Year!

366
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,870
Happy New Year!

367
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:30,000
Lard cakes, pork hock,

368
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:30,840
and pickled cabbage.

369
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:32,630
I've gained weight.

370
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:34,840
No, you haven't!

371
00:15:36,550 --> 00:15:37,200
It's Gao Xiang.

372
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:39,150
He wanted to pick you up,

373
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,270
but I didn't tell him the train.

374
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,870
His biggest flaw

375
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:43,080
is he's overly enthusiastic.

376
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:45,510
On New Year's Eve, both he and my dad

377
00:15:45,510 --> 00:15:46,510
got drunk.

378
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,480
You didn't need to come.

379
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,630
I've already picked up Juan.

380
00:15:53,390 --> 00:15:53,910
What?

381
00:15:54,870 --> 00:15:55,960
Yaodong Apparel?

382
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:57,790
Can't you just

383
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:58,720
wish us well?

384
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:00,480
What's up?

385
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,510
He said there was trouble.

386
00:16:03,150 --> 00:16:03,600
He never

387
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:04,870
trusted Huang Yaodong anyway.

388
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:15,510
Sorry,

389
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:18,080
the number you have dialed is powered off.

390
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:20,550
Sorry, the number you have dialed...

391
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:22,120
It's too late.

392
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,550
Maybe Mr. Huang is asleep.

393
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,150
If he had answered,

394
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,320
I wouldn't even know

395
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:28,550
how to ask him

396
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,510
about these rumors.

397
00:16:38,550 --> 00:16:39,440
Who is it?

398
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,080
Who is it?

399
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:43,910
Coming!

400
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:47,030
I'm coming! Stop knocking!

401
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:50,910
Fang Wanzhi!

402
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,630
My former colleagues told me

403
00:16:53,790 --> 00:16:54,870
that Huang Yaodong ran off

404
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:56,200
with everyone's money.

405
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:57,870
Did he get you too?

406
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:14,510
Huang Yaodong!

407
00:17:15,270 --> 00:17:16,640
You bastard!

408
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,000
You made me

409
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,830
your Southwest distributor

410
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:28,240
and ripped me off for 800,000 RMB!

411
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:31,030
I went begging all my relatives

412
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:33,480
to get that money!

413
00:17:33,550 --> 00:17:36,070
You're ruining me,

414
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:37,110
Huang Yaodong!

415
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,000
Huang Yaodong, pay us back!

416
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,310
Wanzhi!

417
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,160
Wanzhi.

418
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,070
What's done is done.

419
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:11,400
Just calm down.

420
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:13,030
I've reported it to the police.

421
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,680
They've accepted the case.

422
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,030
Unfortunately,

423
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:19,790
you're the biggest victims.

424
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:22,350
Gamblers love

425
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,920
going all in.

426
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:28,750
How could I...

427
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:29,880
My bad.

428
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:33,310
We had our doubts.

429
00:18:34,510 --> 00:18:35,640
We even said

430
00:18:35,790 --> 00:18:37,200
bad character meant no business.

431
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,920
I never expected Huang Yaodong

432
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,750
to be a fraud.

433
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:44,030
This really is on me.

434
00:18:44,790 --> 00:18:46,200
How could it be your fault?

435
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,160
It's my fault.

436
00:18:49,830 --> 00:18:51,270
Gao Xiang warned me,

437
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:53,240
and I didn't listen.

438
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,310
Don't blame yourselves.

439
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,270
Just learn from it.

440
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:00,480
Now,

441
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,400
trust the police

442
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:04,160
and wait patiently.

443
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,790
Perhaps...

444
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:08,920
waiting is agonizing,

445
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,110
but there's no

446
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:12,070
other choice.

447
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,350
I should get going.

448
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,680
My class starts soon.

449
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:42,480
Wang Jia.

450
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,960
She rented the most expensive spot

451
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:47,070
on Hanzheng Street.

452
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,160
The total cost

453
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:51,400
was several hundred thousand.

454
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:57,640
Wanzhi,

455
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,400
I gave Liu Ning strict orders.

456
00:19:59,550 --> 00:20:01,160
The renovation must be finished today.

457
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,030
I'm going to create

458
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:04,550
a flagship store in Wuhan.

459
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,400
When are you shipping the goods?

460
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,000
Remember to come

461
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:08,830
when our shop opens.

462
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:10,030
We'll cut the ribbon.

463
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,200
Listen, Wang Jia.

464
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,640
Something's happened.

465
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:20,480
I really...

466
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:25,000
Sorry I screwed you over.

467
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:34,400
What's up, Wang Jia?

468
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:39,550
Wang Jia?

469
00:20:39,550 --> 00:20:40,550
Don't cry.

470
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:42,640
Wang Jia?

471
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,640
Wang Jia, don't worry.

472
00:20:47,030 --> 00:20:48,030
I'll make up

473
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:49,030
for your losses.

474
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:05,160
Hello?

475
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:08,880
Director Xia.

476
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,440
I'll come this afternoon.

477
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:29,270
When we borrowed the money,
they thanked us

478
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:30,880
for supporting their business.

479
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:32,480
And just a few days later,

480
00:21:32,510 --> 00:21:33,830
they're demanding early repayment!

481
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,310
They probably got wind of

482
00:21:35,310 --> 00:21:36,550
the Yaodong Apparel thing.

483
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,350
What should we do?

484
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:39,790
If we can't pay it back,

485
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:41,200
we'll have to go to jail.

486
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,070
I don't care.

487
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,110
My brother's inside.

488
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:47,270
I'll join him.

489
00:21:47,590 --> 00:21:48,680
Don't bullshit!

490
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:51,440
How can you say that?

491
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:55,200
Wanzhi,

492
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,200
what do we do now?

493
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:14,830
Zhao Jun?

494
00:22:17,070 --> 00:22:18,510
It's convenient

495
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:20,240
to get to my work from here.

496
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:22,240
Only two transfers.

497
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,110
So, you're moving in?

498
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:31,030
I saw there's an empty bed.

499
00:22:31,790 --> 00:22:33,160
You said I could move in.

500
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,270
Does that still stand?

501
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:16,350
Zhao Jun,

502
00:23:17,510 --> 00:23:18,640
I'm bankrupt now.

503
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,510
I'll probably go to jail.

504
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:24,510
So you won't be able

505
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:26,720
to stay here long.

506
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,110
No.

507
00:23:29,790 --> 00:23:31,030
Auntie, you went to college.

508
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:32,400
You're sharp and brave.

509
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:34,310
Nothing can stop you.

510
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:39,960
What did you call me?

511
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:41,750
Auntie.

512
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:44,350
That's right, isn't it?

513
00:23:49,510 --> 00:23:50,830
At Shenxian Peak,

514
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,030
Auntie Xiaoqin was the best to me.

515
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,550
Actually, I'm lucky.

516
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:59,070
All the elders on my mom's side
care about me.

517
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:04,240
She claims you as her family now.

518
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:17,680
Auntie,

519
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:20,310
I borrowed you 300 RMB.

520
00:24:21,070 --> 00:24:22,790
I'm paying you back now, with interest.

521
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:34,880
How much is this?

522
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:36,590
13,000.

523
00:24:37,030 --> 00:24:38,000
Are you crazy?

524
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,720
This is with interest?

525
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,270
I'm a loan shark?

526
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,750
Money doesn't come easy.

527
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:43,750
Save it.

528
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:48,440
I'm drowning in debt.

529
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,070
This wouldn't help.

530
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,000
I know.

531
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,160
But it's all I have.

532
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:57,790
If you see me

533
00:24:57,790 --> 00:24:58,920
as your niece,

534
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,720
just take it.

535
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:09,960
Auntie,

536
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:13,030
I didn't want to drag you down,

537
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:15,720
so I didn't acknowledge you.

538
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:18,350
Now you're in trouble.

539
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:21,790
I wanted you to know you have family.

540
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:43,110
Fang Wanzhi.

541
00:25:43,830 --> 00:25:44,960
Wanna go on a date tonight?

542
00:25:45,750 --> 00:25:46,720
A date? Screw that.

543
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:47,750
Don't you know

544
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:48,960
my situation now?

545
00:25:49,310 --> 00:25:50,440
How can I go on a date?

546
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:52,350
Sorry.

547
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:53,440
Poor choice of words.

548
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,550
Just come have dinner.

549
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,440
Director Xu from the bank will be there.

550
00:26:02,070 --> 00:26:02,830
I'm at school.

551
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,350
Can't talk freely.

552
00:26:05,310 --> 00:26:06,110
Got it.

553
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:07,830
Send me the address.

554
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:09,590
Xiang!

555
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:11,310
You've been gone for ages!

556
00:26:12,310 --> 00:26:12,960
Why so late?

557
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,000
We waited for ages.

558
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,110
Oh, a pretty lady!

559
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,920
No wonder you picked this place.

560
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:19,200
Let me introduce you.

561
00:26:20,070 --> 00:26:21,480
This is my friend, Fang Wanzhi.

562
00:26:21,510 --> 00:26:22,640
This is Director Xu.

563
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:23,590
Hi, Mr. Xu.

564
00:26:23,590 --> 00:26:24,070
Hello.

565
00:26:24,590 --> 00:26:25,400
Let me tell you.

566
00:26:25,830 --> 00:26:27,400
We were in the same class and same dorm.

567
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:28,790
He's stingy.

568
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:30,200
Never offers to pay.

569
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,200
This is the second time.

570
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:33,790
The first time

571
00:26:34,790 --> 00:26:35,880
was when he ditched me

572
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:37,640
to go to grad school.

573
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:38,640
Oh, shut up.

574
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,880
Take a seat.

575
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,160
Just sit.

576
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,270
Please.

577
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:43,920
Xu, is liquor okay?

578
00:26:44,030 --> 00:26:44,480
Sure.

579
00:26:48,110 --> 00:26:48,720
Xiang,

580
00:26:49,510 --> 00:26:50,160
your girlfriend

581
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,510
is so gorgeous.

582
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:53,400
Why not invite

583
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,720
all our classmates

584
00:26:55,790 --> 00:26:57,030
in Shenzhen

585
00:26:57,070 --> 00:26:57,960
and hold a big party?

586
00:26:58,640 --> 00:27:00,000
She's truly gorgeous.

587
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:02,200
But she's my friend,

588
00:27:02,720 --> 00:27:04,110
not my girlfriend.

589
00:27:04,350 --> 00:27:04,920
Here.

590
00:27:07,110 --> 00:27:07,750
I see.

591
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:09,000
You're still

592
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:10,200
pursuing her?

593
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:11,880
Well, let's have a drink.

594
00:27:12,110 --> 00:27:12,440
Sure!

595
00:27:12,550 --> 00:27:12,960
Xu,

596
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,110
you've been warned.

597
00:27:14,270 --> 00:27:15,240
Wanzhi is a good drinker.

598
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:16,510
You might not stand a chance.

599
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:18,750
Really?

600
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:20,480
Perfect.

601
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:21,720
I like a challenge.

602
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:23,550
Come on!

603
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:25,000
Mr. Xu, a toast to you.

604
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,240
Oh, cheers.

605
00:27:26,790 --> 00:27:27,350
Come on.

606
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:28,480
Cheers.

607
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:32,480
You have a master's degree?

608
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:35,880
I've got two now.

609
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,480
The second one is self-taught.

610
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:38,550
So

611
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,590
you should

612
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,000
catch up.

613
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:44,440
I also want to study.

614
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,400
When I first came to Shenzhen,

615
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,440
all I wanted was to make money.

616
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:52,000
I just wanted to support myself.

617
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:54,510
After all that,

618
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:57,480
I'm still in debt.

619
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,880
I don't think

620
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:01,200
you should

621
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:02,920
stress about it too much.

622
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,750
The repayment period

623
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:05,590
is one year.

624
00:28:06,270 --> 00:28:08,000
The bank is pushing for early payment

625
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,350
just because of

626
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,750
Huang Yaodong.

627
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:12,240
Xu promised

628
00:28:12,790 --> 00:28:13,750
he'd put in a good word.

629
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,030
If you pay on time,

630
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:17,240
it shouldn't be a problem.

631
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:19,550
Thank you.

632
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:21,750
Really.

633
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,310
Honestly,

634
00:28:23,750 --> 00:28:25,480
this is partly my fault.

635
00:28:26,550 --> 00:28:27,110
I knew

636
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:28,110
Huang Yaodong was shady.

637
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,720
I regret not being more insistent.

638
00:28:31,440 --> 00:28:32,790
Don't let this get you down.

639
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,350
Every problem

640
00:28:34,720 --> 00:28:35,720
has a solution.

641
00:28:50,510 --> 00:28:51,310
Zhao Jun...

642
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,480
She took me to her factory.

643
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,030
It's not bad.

644
00:28:57,510 --> 00:28:58,350
They're hiring.

645
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,070
Though I have zero experience,

646
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:03,790
the manager said

647
00:29:04,590 --> 00:29:05,510
he'd train me.

648
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,510
It doesn't pay much,

649
00:29:08,070 --> 00:29:09,640
but I believe if we work hard,

650
00:29:10,270 --> 00:29:12,000
we'll pay back the loan.

651
00:29:15,030 --> 00:29:15,920
Why find a job?

652
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,240
Where's the business card?

653
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:24,640
This is yours. This is mine.

654
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:25,200
Tear it up.

655
00:29:26,270 --> 00:29:27,440
I've realized

656
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,200
if you let life beat you

657
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:32,030
and just give up,

658
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,720
it only gets more painful.

659
00:29:35,790 --> 00:29:36,590
Every time

660
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:38,160
I think I can't go on,

661
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,350
if I stick with it a bit more,

662
00:29:41,350 --> 00:29:42,270
I get through it.

663
00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:45,350
I don't want to give up.

664
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:48,310
I want to fight one more time.

665
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,240
How?

666
00:29:52,110 --> 00:29:53,000
We've established

667
00:29:53,030 --> 00:29:54,110
our sales channels.

668
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,790
Clothing companies
in Shenzhen and Dongguan

669
00:29:56,830 --> 00:29:57,920
are the best in the country.

670
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,480
And there's a price difference

671
00:29:59,830 --> 00:30:01,440
between here and inland.

672
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,830
We can't let our hard work

673
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:06,880
go to waste.

674
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:09,480
We busted our asses

675
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,160
to build that sales network

676
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,160
across ten cities.

677
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:14,720
Starting tomorrow,

678
00:30:15,510 --> 00:30:17,400
we'll visit every major garment factory.

679
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,030
Having regular partners

680
00:30:19,030 --> 00:30:20,310
isn't the same

681
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,310
as exclusive deals.

682
00:30:23,830 --> 00:30:25,350
Agency rights are our ticket

683
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:27,350
out of this mess.

684
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,270
There's still hope for us,

685
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:30,440
right?

686
00:30:31,110 --> 00:30:31,790
Of course.

687
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:34,480
(These business cards are worthless now.)

688
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:35,960
(Let's tear them up.)

689
00:30:36,750 --> 00:30:37,790
We can start over.

690
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:15,920
Gao Xiang.

691
00:32:17,350 --> 00:32:18,110
I was about to

692
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:19,270
invite you for a drink.

693
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:21,310
But you were on a business trip.

694
00:32:22,030 --> 00:32:23,070
Oh, that Xu.

695
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:24,960
What are you doing?

696
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:26,200
He got you drunk.

697
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,240
He's dead.

698
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,350
No. Hold on.

699
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:30,830
Mr. Xu was helping me.

700
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:31,720
Don't call him.

701
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:33,640
That was a help?

702
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:35,350
How much did he force on you?

703
00:32:35,640 --> 00:32:36,720
Nobody forced me.

704
00:32:37,310 --> 00:32:38,720
I drank it on my own.

705
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:44,880
Ms. Fang,

706
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:46,160
are you okay?

707
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:47,720
I'm fine.

708
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,590
Let's talk inside.

709
00:32:59,790 --> 00:33:00,550
Have some water.

710
00:33:01,790 --> 00:33:03,000
I did a good job, huh?

711
00:33:04,750 --> 00:33:06,270
Prepaid a million,

712
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:08,680
settled three in interest,

713
00:33:09,550 --> 00:33:10,480
and extended two

714
00:33:11,510 --> 00:33:12,720
for another year.

715
00:33:13,310 --> 00:33:14,160
A million

716
00:33:14,750 --> 00:33:15,590
in six months.

717
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:17,350
You and Li Juan

718
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:18,510
are amazing.

719
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:20,750
Just one more year.

720
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:22,270
I'm confident

721
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:24,000
I can pay off the rest.

722
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,000
Then I should congratulate you.

723
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:30,440
But

724
00:33:30,510 --> 00:33:32,160
Li Juan's tuition was a waste.

725
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:36,310
With sales channels open

726
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:38,750
and transport handled,

727
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,920
we can stop running around.

728
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:42,920
When I return from Yu County,

729
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,590
I'll push Li Juan to start night classes.

730
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:45,920
Rest assured.

731
00:33:46,480 --> 00:33:48,240
I promise I'll make you money.

732
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:50,160
You're going to Yu County?

733
00:33:50,830 --> 00:33:51,550
Yeah.

734
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,160
Train tomorrow.

735
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:56,750
My mom's anniversary.

736
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:04,160
She's been gone

737
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,480
for three years.

738
00:34:18,710 --> 00:34:19,670
That's strange.

739
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:22,550
Someone was just here?

740
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,880
These are offerings for Ms. Fang.

741
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:29,800
My mom said they're blessed.

742
00:34:30,510 --> 00:34:32,440
If you eat them, Ms. Fang will be happy.

743
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:34,150
Yudan?

744
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:36,030
No way.

745
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,840
His sentence isn't up yet.

746
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:58,800
Mrs. Li.

747
00:35:04,550 --> 00:35:05,710
Wanzhi!

748
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,360
You're back!

749
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:10,400
It's been three years!

750
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:13,760
How have you been?

751
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:15,070
I've been well.

752
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,440
And you?

753
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:17,510
Yeah.

754
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,030
I'm doing okay.

755
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:20,920
How's Yudan doing?

756
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:22,230
When will he get out?

757
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,030
He got out a month ago.

758
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:26,510
This morning,

759
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:28,590
we visited Ms. Fang.

760
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,840
I saw the offerings.

761
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:33,550
It really was you.

762
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,440
Where's he?

763
00:35:36,030 --> 00:35:36,510
He's gone.

764
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:37,920
Took the 8:20 train

765
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:38,630
back to school.

766
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:40,840
But his place...

767
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,510
His place?

768
00:35:42,510 --> 00:35:43,190
That's beyond me.

769
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,110
Didn't dare ask.

770
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,550
He just said that.

771
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:46,480
But I think

772
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,110
he's going

773
00:35:47,110 --> 00:35:48,320
to get your address.

774
00:35:50,070 --> 00:35:52,000
Well, just a wild guess.

775
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:08,230
Good!

776
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,880
Wonderful!

777
00:37:05,110 --> 00:37:05,880
Sorry.

778
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,320
I tried,

779
00:37:11,030 --> 00:37:11,800
but couldn't

780
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,190
hold your place.

781
00:37:16,630 --> 00:37:18,190
I know.

782
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,800
Your speech was amazing.

783
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:22,480
All my classmates

784
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:23,550
admire you.

785
00:37:24,230 --> 00:37:25,190
And I get to bask in it.

786
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:28,110
What a great attitude.

787
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:29,670
Better than me.

788
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,590
You did so well

789
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:32,670
on the entrance exam.

790
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,030
You came here

791
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,320
just for me.

792
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,360
But I dragged you down.

793
00:37:40,190 --> 00:37:41,030
I know someone

794
00:37:41,070 --> 00:37:42,320
in continuing education.

795
00:37:43,110 --> 00:37:44,320
He can help you

796
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,360
get your degree

797
00:37:46,710 --> 00:37:47,800
via self-study.

798
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,400
It's hard to find a job

799
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:50,480
without a degree.

800
00:37:51,030 --> 00:37:52,070
I already

801
00:37:52,590 --> 00:37:54,000
got my bachelor's degree.

802
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:55,760
I did it

803
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,920
while I was inside.

804
00:37:57,510 --> 00:37:58,710
I was the only one

805
00:37:58,960 --> 00:38:00,030
in the whole province.

806
00:38:01,030 --> 00:38:02,110
So I became a model

807
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:03,360
and got released early.

808
00:38:08,590 --> 00:38:10,000
Have you gotten a job?

809
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,480
My dad cares about you.

810
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:13,550
He can help you.

811
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:15,230
No need.

812
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:17,630
I'm back at school now.

813
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:20,280
I wanna pursue

814
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,280
a master's in economics.

815
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:22,550
And I've got a professor.

816
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:29,760
You brat.

817
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:32,800
You've already

818
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:33,920
risen from the ashes.

819
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:35,630
So great.

820
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:37,670
Good boy.

821
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:42,510
I really wish

822
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,670
we never met

823
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:47,510
as kids.

824
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:50,480
Why?

825
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:52,880
You regret it?

826
00:38:54,150 --> 00:38:55,440
Blame me for dragging you down?

827
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,880
If we hadn't grown up together.

828
00:39:02,190 --> 00:39:03,480
If we weren't

829
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:05,630
like family,

830
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,110
I'd pursue you.

831
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:14,630
You still said it.

832
00:39:15,590 --> 00:39:16,230
Yeah, I...

833
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:17,550
When I was inside,

834
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,280
I decided

835
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:19,960
I would say it

836
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:20,840
when I got out.

837
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:21,320
I...

838
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:23,230
I won't hold it in anymore.

839
00:39:35,550 --> 00:39:36,280
Fang Wanzhi.

840
00:39:41,670 --> 00:39:42,550
Do I stand a chance?

841
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:54,190
Don't just smile.

842
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:56,670
If there's no chance,

843
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,070
just say it.

844
00:39:58,590 --> 00:39:59,400
I can take it.

845
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:07,510
Yudan,

846
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,150
do you know how much family

847
00:40:13,670 --> 00:40:14,710
means to me?

848
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:25,280
Got it.

849
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:33,550
I got it, Wanzhi.

850
00:40:37,030 --> 00:40:37,590
Cheers.

851
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:22,550
I saw you with the books.

852
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,000
How much did we make?

853
00:41:25,800 --> 00:41:27,030
Gross profit

854
00:41:27,190 --> 00:41:28,280
hit 1.21 million.

855
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:29,840
That's good.

856
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,150
Without the scam,

857
00:41:31,280 --> 00:41:32,590
that would be pretty good.

858
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:36,630
Still owe two million.

859
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,190
That's still not bad anyway.

860
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:42,440
Where the hell is

861
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,760
that damn swindler?

862
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:46,440
Why haven't the cops caught him yet?

863
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:48,920
He's a gambler.

864
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,880
Even if he's caught,

865
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:53,230
the money's probably gone.

866
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:56,960
No dividends this year.

867
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:58,510
Zero return.

868
00:41:59,630 --> 00:42:00,710
Next year too.

869
00:42:01,230 --> 00:42:02,000
Juan,

870
00:42:03,670 --> 00:42:04,920
we'll have to wait

871
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:06,230
to buy a house.

872
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,670
I have patience.

873
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,190
This year

874
00:42:21,550 --> 00:42:22,630
is your animal year.

875
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,880
This was your destined trial.

876
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:31,320
Mr. Zhou...

877
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:35,190
It also happened in my animal year...

878
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:48,920
Right.

879
00:42:49,590 --> 00:42:51,960
My animal year is over now.
